Reference link --> https://spring.io/projects/spring-cloud#overview
NOTE:
Spring Cloud Dependencies version (2020.0.X) is compatible with Spring Boot version (2.4.X)

sample dependency:

<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.springframework.cloud/spring-cloud-dependencies -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.cloud</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-cloud-dependencies</artifactId>
    <version>2020.0.2</version>
    <type>pom</type>
    <scope>runtime</scope>
</dependency>

